---
title: Cal Smart Southwest Beef Skillet with Charred Corn Wild Rice and Pico de Gallo
description: This glorious Southwest-inspired skillet takes things to the next level with a bed of smoky, charred corn tossed with a wild rice medley and topped with spiced beef. Hot peppers offer a mild heat that's tempered by pico de gallo!
